Detailed Description

template<class Base>
class iproc::TSyncProcessorWrap< Base >

Wrapper of iproc::IProcessor for simple synchrone processor implementations.

Assynchrone processing with BeginTask and WaitTaskFinished is redirected to simple synchrone processing by method DoProcessing. All you have to implement from whole interface iproc::IProcessor is method DoProcessing.
